{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-jsx","path":"/post/regain-disqus/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"еЙНи®А\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\" aria-label=\"еЙНи®А permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>еЙНи®А</h2>\n<p>зФ±дЇО Disqus е§ІйЩЖжЧ†ж≥Хж≠£еЄЄиЃњйЧЃпЉМжЙАдї•еЊИйХњдЄАжЃµжЧґйЧіжИСеНЪеЃҐеОЯзФЯзЪД Disqus иѓДиЃЇж°ЖпЉМеП™жЬЙе§ІйЩЖе§ЦеТМгАМжОМжП°зІСе≠¶дЄКзљСгАНжКАиГљзЪДдЇЇпЉМжЙНиГљзЬЛиІБеТМиѓДиЃЇгАВиЃњеЃҐи¶БзХЩи®АпЉМеТМжИСдЇ§жµБйГљеЊЧи¶БгАМзІСе≠¶дЄКзљСгАНеРЧпЉЯе¶ВжЮЬиѓДиЃЇз≥їзїЯдЄНиГљж≠£еЄЄиѓДиЃЇпЉМйВ£ињШи¶БеЃГеє≤еХ•пЉЯеРОжЭ•пЉМжЙЊеИ∞дЇЖжѓФиЊГе•љзЪДиІ£еЖ≥дєЛйБУгАВеП¶е§ЦпЉМ дЄЇдїАдєИе§ІиієеС®зЂ†еЬ∞жКШиЕЊ DisqusпЉМиАМдЄНеОїиѓХиѓХеЫљеЖЕзЪДз±їдЉЉжЬНеК°еСҐпЉЯзЃАеНХжЭ•иѓіпЉМињШжШѓ Disqus еПѓйЭ†дЇЫпЉМињЩдЄНжШѓеіЗжіЛе™Ъе§ЦпЉМдЇЛеЃЮе¶Вж≠§гАВињЩйЗМеЉХзФ® <a href=\"https://imququ.com\">Jerry Qu</a> зЪДдЄАжЃµиѓЭпЉЪ  </p>\n<!-- more -->\n<blockquote>\n<p>дљЬдЄЇдЄАдЄ™еЕНиієдЇІеУБпЉМе¶ВжЮЬдЄНиГљжЙЊеИ∞еПѓйЭ†зЪДзЫИеИ©ж®°еЉПпЉМдїАдєИжЧґеАЩеБЬж≠ҐжЬНеК°е∞±еПЦеЖ≥дЇОиАБжЭњзЪДиАРењГеТМеЖ≥ењГдЇЖгАВ</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"еЃЮзО∞жЦєж≥Х\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95\" aria-label=\"еЃЮзО∞жЦєж≥Х permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>еЃЮзО∞жЦєж≥Х</h2>\n<p>еАЯгАМиЈѓгАНе§ІйЩЖе§ЦзЪДжЬНеК°еЩ®жИЦжФѓжМБ cURL зЪДиЩЪжЛЯз©ЇйЧі(зРЖиЃЇдЄКпЉМе§ІйЩЖеЖЕзЪДзљСзїЬе§Іе§ЪжЧ†ж≥ХзЫіжО•иЃњйЧЃ DisqusпЉМиЩљзДґеПѓдї•дљњзФ®жМЗеЃЪ IPпЉМдљЖиЃњйЧЃ Disqus зЪДйАЯеЇ¶жШОжШЊж≤°жЬЙе§ІйЩЖе§ЦзЪДдЄїжЬЇењЂпЉМжЙАдї•жЬАе•љжШѓе§ІйЩЖе§ЦзЪДдЄїжЬЇ)гАВ<a href=\"https://github.com/fooleap/disqus-php-api\"><strong>disqus-php-api</strong></a> ињЩдЄ™й°єзЫЃе∞±жШѓеРОзЂѓдї£з†БпЉМй°єзЫЃдљЬиАЕйАЙжЛ©дЇЖ PHP cURLпЉМеЫ†дЄЇPHP зЪДиЩЪжЛЯз©ЇйЧіе•љжЙЊеСАгАВ  </p>\n<h2 id=\"еРОзЂѓйГ®зљ≤\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%90%8E%E7%AB%AF%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2\" aria-label=\"еРОзЂѓйГ®зљ≤ permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>еРОзЂѓйГ®зљ≤</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/fooleap/disqus-php-api\"><strong>disqus-php-api</strong></a>  дЄЛ<code class=\"language-text\">api</code>зЫЃељХдЄЛзЪДе∞±жШѓ PHP еРОеП∞дї£з†БгАВ  </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">вФЬвФАdisqus-php-api\nвФВ      demo.html\nвФВ      gulpfile.js\nвФВ      index.js\nвФВ      package.json\nвФВ      update-thread.html\nвФВ      webpack.config.js\nвФВ\nвФЬвФАapi\nвФВ  вФВ  cacert.pem\nвФВ  вФВ  config.php\nвФВ  вФВ  count.php\nвФВ  вФВ  createthread.php\nвФВ  вФВ  getcomments.php\nвФВ  вФВ  getgravatar.php\nвФВ  вФВ  init.php\nвФВ  вФВ  popular.php\nвФВ  вФВ  postcomment.php\nвФВ  вФВ  removecomment.php\nвФВ  вФВ  sendemail.php\nвФВ  вФВ  updatecomment.php\nвФВ  вФВ  updatethread.php\nвФВ  вФВ  upload.php\nвФВ  вФВ\nвФВ  вФЬвФАemojione\nвФВ  вФВ  вФВ  autoload.php\nвФВ  вФВ  вФВ\nвФВ  вФВ  вФФвФАsrc\nвФВ  вФВ          Client.php\nвФВ  вФВ          ClientInterface.php\nвФВ  вФВ          Emojione.php\nвФВ  вФВ          Ruleset.php\nвФВ  вФВ          RulesetInterface.php\nвФВ  вФВ\nвФВ  вФФвФАPHPMailer\nвФВ          class.phpmailer.php\nвФВ          class.smtp.php\nвФВ\nвФЬвФАdist\nвФВ      eac.min.json\nвФВ      iDisqus.min.css\nвФВ      iDisqus.min.js\nвФВ\nвФФвФАsrc\n       eac.json\n       iDisqus.js\n       iDisqus.scss\n       jsonminify</code></pre></div>\n<p>жМЙзЕІ<code class=\"language-text\">config.php</code>жЦЗдїґйЗМзЪДдї£з†Бж≥®йЗКпЉМе∞ЖзЫЄеЕ≥дЄ™дЇЇ Disqus  йЕНзљЃдњ°жБѓе°Ђе•љгАВзДґеРОе∞±зЫіжО•жККжХідЄ™<code class=\"language-text\">api</code>жЦЗдїґе§єжЛЈиіЭеИ∞иЗ™еЈ±зЪДеҐГе§ЦжЬНеК°еЩ®жИЦиАЕ PHP иЩЪжЛЯз©ЇйЧігАВиЗ≥ж≠§пЉМеРОзЂѓе∞±йГ®зљ≤е•љдЇЖгАВ</p>\n<p><strong>ж≥®</strong>пЉЪе¶ВжЮЬдљњзФ®зЪДжШѓиЩЪжЛЯ PHP з©ЇйЧіпЉМж≠§ PHP API зЪД URL еПѓдї•дљњзФ®иЩЪжЛЯз©ЇйЧіжПРдЊЫзЪДдЇМзЇІеЯЯеРНпЉМдєЯеПѓдї•дљњзФ®иЗ™еЈ±зЪДеЯЯеРНпЉМURL зЪДеЬ∞еЭАеПѓдї•иІДиМГдЄАдЄЛпЉМжѓФе¶ВпЉЪ<code class=\"language-text\">//api.xxx.com/disqus/v1</code>гАВ  </p>\n<h2 id=\"еЙНзЂѓдљњзФ®\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\" aria-label=\"еЙНзЂѓдљњзФ® permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>еЙНзЂѓдљњзФ®</h2>\n<p>еЙНзЂѓйЬАи¶Б <a href=\"https://github.com/fooleap/disqus-php-api\"><strong>disqus-php-api</strong></a> дЄЛ<code class=\"language-text\">dist</code>зЫЃељХдЄЛзЪДдЄЙдЄ™жЦЗдїґпЉЪ<code class=\"language-text\">eac.min.json</code>(еОЛзЉ©зЪД emoji unicode зЉЦз†БжЦЗдїґ)пЉМ<code class=\"language-text\">iDisqus.min.css</code>пЉМ<code class=\"language-text\">iDisqus.min.js</code>гАВ  </p>\n<p>дЄїи¶БеИЖдЄЙж≠•пЉЪ</p>\n<ul>\n<li>еЉХеЕ• CSS, JSпЉЪ </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>link</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">rel</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>stylesheet<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>path/to/iDisqus.min.css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>path/to/iDisqus.min.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>еИЫеїЇеЃєеЩ®пЉЪ</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>comment<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>еИЫеїЇеЃЮдЊЛпЉЪ</li>\n</ul>\n<p>ињЩйЗМиііеЗЇжИСзЪДе§ІдљУйЕНзљЃпЉМиѓ¶зїЖе¶ВдљХйЕНзљЃеПВзЬЛ <a href=\"https://github.com/fooleap/disqus-php-api/blob/master/readme.md\">README</a>гАВ</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> disq <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">iDisqus</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'comment'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    forum<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'your_disqus_short_name'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    api<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'https://api.xxx.com/disqus/v1'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    site<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'https://your_website.com'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    mode<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    timeout<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">3000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    init<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    toggle<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'comment-toggle'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    sort<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'newest'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    emoji_preview<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\tbadge<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'еНЪдЄї'</span>\n <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ndisq<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">popular</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ndisq<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">count</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>еѓєдЇОеИЗжНҐиѓДиЃЇж°ЖпЉМеЕЈдљУзФ®ж≥ХжШѓеЬ®зљСй°µдЄ≠жФЊзљЃдЄАдЄ™ Checkbox пЉЪ</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>comment-toggle<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> \n\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</sp